This dashboard shows an overview of detailed information about the Email and it's file and URL related activity on Network.

Please visit the [Email Activity](https://schema.ocsf.io/1.1.0/classes/email_activity), [Email File Activity](https://schema.ocsf.io/1.1.0/classes/email_file_activity) and [Email URL Activity](https://schema.ocsf.io/1.1.0/classes/email_url_activity) documentation for more information.
